    "bio_exists": true,
    "bio_summary": "Sofiane Pamart is a French pianist, based in Paris and originally from Hellemmes in the suburbs of Lille. He is known to the French public for breaking the elitist codes of classical piano.\n\nAs a gold medallist at the Conservatoire de Lille, he took a different track from the typical classical music path. Alongside his solo career, he is renowned as a go-to pianist in the French rap scene. He has collaborated with French rappers, including Koba LaD, Vald, Maes, Sneazzy, Hugo TSR, Scylla, Lord Es",
